..TEXT:
|al monte ove ragion ne fruga~: Compare ^Inf.~ XXX,
70.  ^Frugare~ can mean "to goad" (cf. ^Purg.~ XIV, 39; XV,
137), but here it is best understood in the sense of "probe."
|ragion~: God's justice.
